{"tid":970442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[傻閪環保撚]連登仔老豆買左幾包飲管派，俾傻閪環保撚圍爐guoup搞走塑批鬥，仲話佢老豆垃圾","createTime":"2019-01-05T20:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T06:21:33.000Z","uid":38795,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f13e5b220ad21c862c7f6be62fa15db0d3bfc74a","tid":970442,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T20:39:29.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/969316/page/11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/969316/page/11</a><br />\n老豆癲左 買左幾包飲管派<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1683370671991485/permalink/2194640130864534/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1683370671991485%2Fpermalink%2F2194640130864534%2F&d=rCC6LyfnNA3Id4pBenNlAY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=31a7421d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1683370671991485/permalink/2194640130864534/</a><br />\n班傻閪環保撚圍爐guoup搞走塑睇到後批鬥樓主<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omEeJhN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomEeJhN.png&h=60c2a3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WBDi9XO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWBDi9XO.png&h=02194794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余珮環仲話樓主老豆垃圾<br />\n余珮環<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/michelle.yu01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmichelle.yu01&d=rCC6LyfnNA3Id4pBenNlAY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ab58249a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/michelle.yu01</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WX4k6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WX4k6o.jpg&h=29d3043a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6coBEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6coBEK.jpg&h=3374dedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/